","text":"When Ultralite.requestControl with a .scroll layout type .. this is the class you interate with to draw scrolling text to the screen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Once the layout is .scrolled you must send one configure message to tell the layout how to setup.  It will setup the slice height and how many slices are visible.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are two supported modes: autoScroll on\/off"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is true, the slices are automatically scrolled.  Subscribe to the delgate and listen for the scrolled callback, when you get it send another slice of text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When autoScroll is false, you can drive the slices and how they look on the screen.  You can send all the slices at once or send one at a time and animate it onto the screen at the current time.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout","role":"symbol"},"doc://ultralitesdk.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/Action/init(rawValue:)":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/ultralitesdk.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/Action\/init(rawValue:)","title":"init(rawValue:)","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/action\/init(rawvalue:)","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"rawValue"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://ultralitesdk.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK":{"title":"UltraliteSDK","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk","identifier":"doc:\/\/ultralitesdk.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this SDK to easily send text and images to your Vuxix smart glasses."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collecti